Hey There, and welcome to Limelight!

We're glad you've decided to join! Here are a few tips to get you started.

1. Follow Some Topics
Go find topics that interest you! Then follow them and have related posts show up in your feed.

2. Contribute
Find something cool on the web that you want to share? Have something to say? That's what Limelight is for, just click "+Post" up top!

3. Interact
Join the discussion - rate, share, and talk about posts. Talk with friends and people with similar interests about topics you like.


If you have any questions or comments simply add the "Limelight Feedback" topic to a post. You can also reach us directly on Limelight @Marc and @Matt.